Finance Agreement :Project reporting | Description :The Recipient shall cause the Project Implementing Entity to monitor andevaluate the progress of the Project and prepare Project Reports in accordance with the provisions of Section 4.08 of the GeneralConditions and on the basis of the indicators agreed with the Association. | Frequency :Yearly
